(11, 'Rob', 'rswoods@swva.net', 'revtfore2#L', '97Hj7VYS7cw27aFVadyp5pcJBxm3Ia', 'No Highlight~Favorite~Important!~Question~Correction~Errata', null, 1, '1:1:1:1:1:1:2', 'Rob W', '2023-05-14 17:04:13', '172.93.60.8', null, '0:0:12:14:-1:0~14:3:7:0:0:0~0:0:12:14:-1:0~3:2:2:4:zeph_4:0:1~3:2:2:3:zeph_4:0:1~3:2:2:4:zeph_4:0:0~0:0:12:14:25:0~3:2:1:1:jonah:0:0~0:1:40:1:-1:0~41:-1:0:0:0:0~0:1:40:1:-1:0~41:-1:0:0:0:0~0:1:40:1:-1:0~10:1:48:0:0:0~10:1:46:0:0:0~10:1:48:0:0:0~3:2:1:1:com_rom_nav4:0:0~0:1:45:2:-1:0~0:1:45:1:-1:0~4:1:45:3:-1:0~3:2:1:1:com_rom_nav3:0:0~4:1:45:3:-1:0~3:2:1:1:rom1:0:0~0:1:45:1:-1:0~0:0:39:4:-1:0~0:1:40:1:-1:0', '0,1,43,1,nav4;0,0,39,3,nav3;5,1,46,2,8;0,1,40,24,nav26;5,1,62,2,6;5,1,43,3,3;44,-1,0,1,0;0,1,40,24,0;0,1,40,26,0;14,3,12,1,1;14,3,4,1,1', '<p>My personal Reviewer workspace</p>', '<p>Having wrong doctrine keeps you from searching for right doctrine.</p> <h2>REV TODO List</h2> <p><span style="color:#E74C3C;">TODO:</span></p> <ul> <li>Finish sops</li> <li>Make sure all settings are on the settings page</li> <li>Look into exporting WS&rsquo;s to ES, MS, SS, etc.</li> <li>Scripture refs do not work in margin notes on mobile devices. When tapped, the editor opens instead.</li> <li>instructions for bib &amp; abbr edit page</li> <li>---</li> <li><span style="color:#e74c3c;">!!!</span> figure out why tracking for info or appx <u><em>sometimes</em></u> shows the whole doc as new.</li> </ul> <p><span style="color:#e74c3c;">MAYB:</span></p> <ul> <li>fix findwordstudy to find &ldquo;word study on <em>adelphos.</em>&rdquo; May not be doable&hellip;</li> <li>add published flag for book intros</li> <li>Try updating the parent directly rather than calling jsonmyrevtasks. Save calls to the server.</li> </ul> <p><span style="color:#E74C3C;">DONE:</span></p> <ul> <li>Implement visibility toggle [checkbox] for MyREV margin notes.</li> <li>implement sops off/on setting.</li> <li>Smart quotes in margin note editor</li> <li>Install editor for margin notes.</li> <l